<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.10.3">
<l>payaṉalla ceytu payaṉillai neñcē</l>
<l>puyaṉmaḻai vaṇṇar purintuṟai kōyiṉ</l>
<l>mayaṉmiku poḻilcūḻ māliruñ cōlai</l>
<l>yayaṉmalai yaṭaiva tatuka rumamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Doing good for benefit is no benefit, heart.</l>
<l>Reaching the mountain in the neighbourhood</l>
<l>of Māliruñcōlai surrounded by pleasure groves,</l>
<l>the temple where desirously stays the one the colour of rain clouds,</l>
	<l>that is [good] action/karma.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
